---
// src/components/Community.astro
---
<section class="section-mid py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-5">
        <span class="w-8 h-px bg-amber-400/40"></span>
        <span class="font-body text-amber-500 text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase">Siyakhathalela</span>
        <span class="w-8 h-px bg-amber-400/40"></span>
      </div>
      <span class="gold-line mx-auto"></span>
      <h2 class="section-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-white">
        We Don’t Just <span class="text-amber-400">Host Nights.</span><br>
        We Build Community.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        A portion of everything we earn at eKoneni goes back into Mdantsane. Here are some of the real stories behind our community work.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stories -->
    <div class="space-y-14">

      <!-- Story 1 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-amber-400/10 aspect-video bg-zinc-900 flex items-center justify-center">
          <!-- Placeholder - Replace with real feeding scheme photo -->
          <img src="https://placehold.co/800x450/1f2937/9ca3af?text=Insert+Feeding+Scheme+Photo" 
               alt="Placeholder - Feeding Scheme" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-4">Feeding Scheme – Winter 2025</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            We partnered with local families to prepare and deliver warm meals to over 120 children in NU1 and NU2 during the cold months. Many of these kids would have gone to bed hungry without this support.
          </p>
          <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
            Read full story →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Story 2 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-4">Rebuilding Homes – 2025</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            After a family lost their home to a fire, we mobilised resources and labour to help rebuild. The family is now safe and back in their community. This is what eKoneni stands for.
          </p>
          <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
            Read full story →
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-amber-400/10 aspect-video bg-zinc-900 flex items-center justify-center order-1 lg:order-2">
          <!-- Placeholder - Replace with real home rebuilding photo -->
          <img src="https://placehold.co/800x450/1f2937/9ca3af?text=Insert+Home+Rebuilding+Photo" 
               alt="Placeholder - Home Rebuilding" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Story 3 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-amber-400/10 aspect-video bg-zinc-900 flex items-center justify-center">
          <!-- Placeholder - Replace with real community support photo -->
          <img src="https://placehold.co/800x450/1f2937/9ca3af?text=Insert+Community+Support+Photo" 
               alt="Placeholder - Community Support" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-4">Youth &amp; Family Support</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            We regularly support local youth programs and assist families going through difficult times with groceries, school supplies, and emotional support. The lounge has become more than a party spot — it’s a pillar in the community.
          </p>
          <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
            Read full story →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Final Message + CTA -->
    <div class="mt-16 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-lg">
        When you celebrate at eKoneni, you’re helping us take care of our people. This is our promise to Mdantsane.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="#contact" 
           class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400 text-black font-medium tracking-wide text-sm hover:bg-amber-300 transition-colors">
          Support our community work →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>